14:00.title: AutoML - Introduction, Use Cases and Demo
14:00.description: Cloud AutoML is a suite of machine learning products that enables developers with limited machine learning expertise to train high-quality models specific to their business needs. It relies on Google’s state-of-the-art transfer learning and neural architecture search technology. In this session we will go through what's available in this suite.

14:40.title: 把 Ktor 部署到 Google Cloud 去 Jetbrains
14:40.description: Ktor 是由 JetBrains 以 100% Kotlin 打造的 Web 框架，其簡潔輕量、易懂好學的設計，讓其非常適合用於網路服務的開發。不過許多新手在學會 Ktor 後最常問的問題，就是該怎麼部署到雲端？在這場分享裡，將會分享如何將 Ktor 打包成 Container Image 後部署上雲。
